item.title: Tryouts 2024
item.description: Our first tryout took place in Prosetin. There were a lot of firsts: We got together for the first time of the season, first time outside, first time with new coaches. It was a productive weekend, working of motion offence and re-learning to not get lost in a lobster trap and avoid middle-school passes. The start of our journey to EUCF 2024 was great, the athmosphere is electrifying and we’re ready to bring the best of Czech ultimate onto the best European teams!
